@startuml
title [RF013] - Lista de Espera de Adotantes

actor ONG as "Admin ONG"
participant UI as "Interface UI"
participant Backend as "Back End"
database DB as "Banco de Dados"

ONG ->> UI: Solicita lista de interessados
UI ->> Backend: GET /api/animais/{id}/interesses
Backend ->> DB: SELECT usuarios FROM interesses WHERE animal_id=...
DB -->> Backend: Lista de interessados
Backend -->> UI: Retorna lista
UI -->> ONG: Exibe lista
@enduml
